description._content: Description: Basement Showing Installation of Pipes. The New Government Hospital, Haifa. Location: Haifa, Palestine Date: 1940 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/741 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
